{"id":92082,"title":"Sport-related eye injury in northern Israel.","abstract":"Eye injuries are common in sports. Sports-related eye injuries have the potential for major morbidityTo investigate the occurrence and to classify sport-related eye trauma in northern Israel.We analyzed the records of the ophthalmology emergency department for the years 2007-2011 and classified the admissions according to type, severity of injury and demographic data.In 2% of the patients the injuries occurred during a sport activity. Most of the injuries occurred during soccer, basketball or school sport activity (74%). The majority of patients were young males.Most sports-related eye injuries can be prevented with adequate eye protection.","date":"2014-01-23","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24449981","annotations":[{"name":"Ophthalmology","weight":0.721475,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ophthalmology"},{"name":"Israel","weight":0.670807,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Israel"},{"name":"Basketball","weight":0.582528,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basketball"},{"name":"Emergency department","weight":0.50256,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emergency_department"},{"name":"Human eye","weight":0.492145,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_eye"},{"name":"Association football","weight":0.460745,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Association_football"},{"name":"Trauma (medicine)","weight":0.2352,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trauma_(medicine)"},{"name":"Injury","weight":0.210873,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Injury"},{"name":"Sport","weight":0.210873,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sport"},{"name":"Demographics","weight":0.204122,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Demographics"},{"name":"School","weight":0.107046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/